{"tid":400742,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"那年，中華武士會成立。","createTime":"2017-09-15T05:16:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T09:40:20.000Z","uid":126293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"120cf3b4a5f1bf90d8ad650ff4d3d0ecd58d4f89","tid":400742,"uid":126293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T05:16:05.000Z","msg":"那年，中華武士會成立。<br />\n從南方來了一個人，話不多說，手中拿着一塊餅，讓我大師兄李存義掰開。<br />\n我師兄李存義沒有說話，還讓他當了武士會的第一任會長。<br />\n他憑的不是武功，是一句話：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>拳有南北，國有南北嗎？!</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695654b9e8ee5526a295556cd46bade9ef84d90c","tid":400742,"uid":126293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T05:18:15.000Z","msg":"其實天下之大，又何止南北。勉強求全，等於固步自封。<br />\n在你眼中在，這塊餅是個武林。對我來講是一個世界。<br />\n所謂大成若缺，有缺憾才能有進步。<br />\n真管用的話，南拳又何止北傳。你說對嗎？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9a1d9833b26d8980c6e81889f5f72b51a2ca522","tid":400742,"uid":126293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T05:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/15/132005_5e3184354e1f7bcf47e768368a9d9752.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F15%2F132005_5e3184354e1f7bcf47e768368a9d9752.jpg&h=561719f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n葉先生，今日我把名聲送給你，往後的路，你是一步一擂臺。<br />\n希望你像我一樣，拼一口氣，點一盞燈。<br />\n要知道念念不忘，必有迴響 ! 有燈就有人。"},{"pid":"0e117c70a2c55e4000acbdba926a1ac2940c1a2c","tid":400742,"uid":126293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T05:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://image.zixundingzhi.com/7-ccyup0Ijfp_SkCrkMiMRBJO3A=/full/9291954d8388f46f4f145fea46290e4837879e06\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.zixundingzhi.com%2F7-ccyup0Ijfp_SkCrkMiMRBJO3A%3D%2Ffull%2F9291954d8388f46f4f145fea46290e4837879e06&h=c79385ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c87265d668797f4787f54ab5e0622eeaee51f4c6","tid":400742,"uid":126293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T05:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://imglf1.nosdn.127.net/img/MHpBcUg3UEhhYWs1M20xTWZ4eUpldGZYbllUQVZVbExudDVNK2NHNnhJanFrSVBXblYvdnpBPT0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimglf1.nosdn.127.net%2Fimg%2FMHpBcUg3UEhhYWs1M20xTWZ4eUpldGZYbllUQVZVbExudDVNK2NHNnhJanFrSVBXblYvdnpBPT0.gif&h=805a3006&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f37b170888ae8d55bc94e18da1e5e94402e6e664","tid":400742,"uid":40198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T08:47:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/15/164721_9bff0c3964b8d7f4d21a5c0716baeebb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F15%2F164721_9bff0c3964b8d7f4d21a5c0716baeebb.jpg&h=da5aff02&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"558ab8ef2d6eb52fa2e4eda4b98891d396b1eec2","tid":400742,"uid":126293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T09:40:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/15/164721_9bff0c3964b8d7f4d21a5c0716baeebb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F15%2F164721_9bff0c3964b8d7f4d21a5c0716baeebb.jpg&h=da5aff02&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}